reviews.review_text:
Pretty Sweet Show This is a real nice sounding aud. Good setlist and all the songs are played well. I put off downloading the Charlie Miller 5/18/72 to get this. Yeah, I think it sounds that good. It has a good balance between the crowd and the band. Thanks for the upload Mr. Grabski. Get it, I think you'll dig it. 
Everybody hang loose.
